task.summary: Fix card labels pushing images upwards.

Merge branch 'master' of bitbucket.org:tachiweb/tachiweb-ui
Conflicts: TachiWeb/index.html
Categories are now headings (dynamic tabs are not support by MDL).
Fix filter button not hiding and showing when selecting different tabs.
Switching tabs now changes the text of the refresh button.
Fix read page text not centering.
Remove animation when resizing browser window. Fix typo.
Fixed compatibility with new server update.

Add mark as read/unread in manga info page. Added restore/backup page. Implemented favorite button. You can now drag/pan zoomed in images in the reader. The reader now updates reading positions and statuses on the server. Code cleanup. Remove old TODOs.
Reader now mimics Tachiyomi behavior when setting reading positions.
Marking a chapters as unread now automatically resets it's last read page.
Add chapter and manga info updating.
The navigation drawer is now populated in JS.
Finish preliminary catalogue. Many bug fixes.

Add slider and page indicator. Fix keyboard controls scrolling the wrong direction when RTL mode is on. Added drawer to restore/backup page. Added restore/backup page to drawer. Fix catalogue URLs not being encoded. Fix page skipping when loading more than one page of manga in the catalogue.
